Package com.enh.lmsclient

Class AppConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.enh.lmsclient.AppConfig
  • public class AppConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the configuration for the LMS client application. It loads configuration properties from a "config.properties" file and provides access methods to retrieve specific configuration values.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor Description
      AppConfig()
      Constructs an AppConfig instance and loads the configuration properties from the "config.properties" file.
